trans-unit.source: Describes the possible values for the status of a <xref href="System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Descreve os possíveis valores para o status de um <xref href="System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation> is returned after a call to <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.BeginInvoke%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation>é retornada após uma chamada para <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.BeginInvoke%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.BeginInvoke%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation> can be used to interact with the delegate on the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> queue, such as changing the priority of the operation or aborting the operation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation>pode ser usado para interagir com o delegado no <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher>fila, como alterar a prioridade da operação ou anular a operação.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> </xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation>

trans-unit.source: The stages of a <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation> are Pending, Executing, and Completed.
trans-unit.target: Os estágios de um <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation>Aguardando, executando e concluído.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherOperation>

trans-unit.source: At any point before the operation completes, the status can be set to Aborted.
trans-unit.target: A qualquer momento antes da conclusão da operação, o status pode ser definido para Aborted.

trans-unit.source: The operation started executing, but has not completed.
trans-unit.target: A operação de início da execução, mas não foi concluída.

trans-unit.source: The operation is pending and is still in the <xref href="System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher"></xref> queue.
trans-unit.target: A operação está pendente e ainda estiver no <xref href="System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher"> </xref> fila.
